title: KSI admits he was “washed” on YouTube after struggling to hit one million views
summary_full: British creator KSI openly admitted to a difficult period on YouTube in mid-2025, where his videos struggled to reach one million views, leading him to feel "fallen off." Despite external successes, he recommitted to the platform, and his main channel has since seen view counts surpass the one million mark, indicating a gradual comeback.
